{% block body %}
  <strong>Next steps:</strong>
  <ul>
    <li>If you received the CERB through Service Canada, do not apply for EI. We will contact you provide more information.</li>
    <li>If you received the CERB through the Canada Revenue Agency or if you never received the CERB, you will have to apply for EI.</li>
    <li>If you received the CERB and are not sure which department you applied through, <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/services/benefits/ei/cerb-application.html#contact">contact us</a>.</li>
  </ul>
{% endblock %}

